text: Taco Time (or TacoTime) is an American fast-food restaurant chain. It sells Mexican-American food. It has over 226 restaurants in the United States and 74 restaurants in Western Canada. It was founded in Eugene, Oregon, in 1960 by Ron Fraedrick. ==References== Category:Companies based in Oregon Category:American fast food restaurants Category:20th-century establishments in Oregon Category:1960 establishments in the United States
